HaTeMiLe for Java 2.2.0 API

Packages 
Package Description
org.hatemile
The org.hatemile package contains the interfaces with the acessibility solutions.
org.hatemile.implementation
The org.hatemile.implementation package contains the official implementation of interfaces solutions.
org.hatemile.util
The org.hatemile.util package contains the utilities of library.
org.hatemile.util.css
The org.hatemile.util.css package contains the interfaces of CSS handles.
org.hatemile.util.css.phcss
The org.hatemile.util.css.phcss package contains the implementation of CSS handles for ph-css library.
org.hatemile.util.html
The org.hatemile.util.html package contains the interfaces of HTML handles.
org.hatemile.util.html.jsoup
The org.hatemile.util.html.jsoup package contains the implementation of HTML handles for Jsoup library.
